HEADWORD: Desilverization
<hw>De*sil`ver*i*za"tion</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The act
or the process of freeing from silver; also, the condition resulting
from the removal of silver.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

